msgctxt "84_Chief Executive Officer"
msgid "My head's going to explode... Must've had too much to drink last night. Could you go see if they've got anything for a hangover at Kotobuki Drugs over there?"
msgstr "Me duele muchísimo la cabeza... Seguro tomé demasiado anoche. ¿Podrías ir a ver si tienen algo para la resaca en la Farmacia Kotobuki de allá?"

msgctxt "96_Section Chief"
msgid "You sure you're okay, sir? You were still doing shots at sunrise... Maybe you should take the day off."
msgstr "¿Seguro que se siente bien, señor? Aún estaba tomando tragos al amanecer... Tal vez debería tomarse el día libre."

msgctxt "108_Chief Executive Officer"
msgid "What choice did I have? We have to keep our customers happy when we take them out. That's part of the job."
msgstr "¿Qué opción tenía? Tenemos que mantener a nuestros clientes felices cuando los sacamos. Eso es parte del trabajo."

msgctxt "120_Section Chief"
msgid "I know, I know! I mean, thanks to your hard work－and drinking－we got them to sign that contract."
msgstr "¡Lo sé, lo sé! Quiero decir, gracias a su arduo trabajo—y a beber—logramos que firmaran ese contrato."

msgctxt "132_Section Chief"
msgid "So, what will it be!? Staminan or Tauriner? I'll get you anything you want!"
msgstr "¿Entonces, cuál quiere? ¿Staminan o Tauriner? ¡Yo se lo consigo!"

